Description: Logic circuit simulator focused on education
 wiRedPanda is free software designed to help students learn about
 logic circuits and simulate them in an easy and friendly way.
 .
 Features include real-time logic simulation, a user-friendly interface,
 and support for exporting circuits as images or PDFs.
